data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Foot Hills neighborhood. This home is right next to Ivywild, Broadmoor, and Cheyenne Mountain. This charming residence offers a perfect blend of convenience and comfort. Immerse yourself in the ease of living with proximity to shopping centers, ensuring all your daily needs are met effortlessly. The landscaping of the property boasts a vibrant display of native flowers, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step inside to discover the thoughtful upgrades that make this home stand out, being welcomed into the open concept home with LVP floors. Hardwood flooring graces two rooms and the hallway, providing a timeless and durable foundation. The primary bedroom features laminate flooring, offering both style and practicality. The home is flooded with natural light, including the five new 2020 Wingard custom windows, showcasing a commitment to modern design and energy efficiency. Stay comfortable year-round with the peace of mind that comes from having both the AC and furnace replaced in 2021. The backyard features a pergola perfect for enjoying the warm Colorado Summers! Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home in a prime location!
